# Engineers — Frontend SPA

Vite + React 18 + TypeScript single-page app. Talks to the [`engineers_backend`](https://github.com/super-dev-vibe/engineers_backend) FastAPI service over REST + Server-Sent Events. Tailwind for styling, SWR for data, react-router-dom for routing, react-hot-toast for notifications.

## Features

- **Auth** — register / login against the FastAPI `/auth/*` endpoints. JWT bearer tokens stored in localStorage. First user to register against an empty database becomes `admin`.
- **Three roles** with different navigation: `admin` (full access), `staff` (own data only), `accountant` (only `/accountants`).
- **Modules** — Dashboard, Accounts (with resume uploads), Transactions, Card Links, Weekly Plan, Users (admin), Interviews.
- **Interview Review with AI** — pick interviews, run admin-managed Skills (one-shot prompts) or your own custom prompt against OpenAI. Output streams live via SSE; every run is persisted so reloads are instant.
- **Resume parsing** — client-side PDF / Markdown → markdown via `pdfjs-dist`, rendered safely with `marked` + `DOMPurify`.

